SomniaAgentConsumer::sweep
├── when the caller is not the owner
│   └── it should revert with NotOwner.
└── when the caller is the owner
    ├── when the recipient is the zero address
    │   └── it should revert with ZeroRecipient.
    └── when the recipient is non-zero
        ├── it should transfer the full contract balance to the recipient.
        ├── it should return the swept amount.
        └── it should leave the contract balance at zero.

# Egress (B-1 fix). receive() is the only value inflow on the reusable base; without an
# outflow every platform rebate / over-fund surplus would be permanently trapped. sweep()
# is the base-level rescue (owner set at deploy). Subclasses with real escrow accounting
# govern egress themselves. CEI-safe: no state mutated after the external call.
